Package: vera-desktop
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libvera-xsettings0, libvera0 (= ${binary:Version})
Description: Next-generation GTK+3 Desktop Environment - main binaries
 vera is a next generation GTK+3 desktop environment built for Semplice
 Linux.
 .
 This package contains the main binaries, along with the session files.

